OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy this
OL,6,Fevening with a little drizzle in
OL,7,Fplaces. Then it will remain cloudy
OL,8,Fovernight with some patchy drizzle,
OL,9,Fthis mainly across the west. Light
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry and rather cloudy day,
OL,13,Fbut some bright or sunny spells will
OL,14,Fbreak through during the afternoon.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,17,Fto Wednesday dry with sunny spells,
OL,18,Fsome overnight cloud or fog. Becoming
OL,19,Fwarm or very warm inland but staying
OL,20,Fcooler around the coast.
